    job_description:
      "Are you opened to new and exciting challenges? TMC is looking for Front-End Developers to join our Software Factory. Be part of our team whose culture celebrates collaboration, learning, constructive debate, innovation and creativity. Would you like to know more?\n\n| YOUR CHALLENGES?\n\nWe are currently seeking flexible and fast-thinking Front-End Developers. We have open positions for you in New Zealand, Spain and Portugal. Would you like to be part of a world-class team developing innovative projects for International brand clients using the latest technology?\n\nWe focus on delivering quality work, supporting our customers and above all, attitude! That’s why we expect our people to feel at home in all areas of today’s development.\n\n| WHAT DO WE EXPECT FROM YOU?\n\nYou have a BSc. or MSc. Degree in Computer Sciences, Informatics or related field required with 5+ years of experience in Front-End development. During your MSc. or through professional experience you have gained expertise in one or more of the following topics:\n• Experience reading, writing, reviewing JavaScript and/or TypeScript code.\n• Consolidated knowledge in modern frameworks such as React and Angular\n• Experience with the most popular open-source mobile application framework in order to build mobile applications (React Native)\n• Worked on products rather than just in projects. You understand market success, customer satisfaction and aim everything towards it.\n• Familiarity with Agile development frameworks, e.g. Scrum\n• Fluent in English is essential\n\n| WHAT DOES OUR BUSINESS CELL HAVE TO OFFER?\n\nBe part of the TMC Software Factory, our Development Center that provides IT expertise and development based on best practices and accumulated experience to all our clients. We excel in agile development and IT engineering.\n\nWho we are?\n• High Performance Development Center\n• Technological solutions tailored-fit for each customer\n• Capability to work with a variety of technologies\n• Software quality & security compliance best practices\n• Continuous delivery to customers\n• Cybersecurity compliance\n• We invest in technological surveillance\n\n| WHAT CAN YOU EXPECT FROM TMC?\n\nTMC is an international high-tech consultancy company that brings expertise to their clients in order to support them with the realization of their technological challenges. As such, TMC is operating as an expert center at the disposition of its clients and we help them to be more competitive in an ever more global and faster changing technological world.\n\nAt TMC we believe that people are the driving force behind technological innovation. That is why we want to create the best possible conditions for tech talents to thrive in. We offer you a challenging and stimulating work environment in which you can be the director of your own career.\n\nAs an Employeneur you are part of our TMC family. Next to our outstanding technical expertise, fun and engagement are meaningful parts of our culture.\n\n| WHY CHOOSE FOR EMPLOYENEURSHIP?\n\nWe are truly unique thanks to our Employeneurship model which is a true innovation for the High Technology consulting business. It is the business relationship of the 21th century for high skilled technical professionals. It is built around 5 main pillars:\n• You will have a permanent employment contract, offering you stability and security\n• You will get to know your market value and have a share in the profit your work generates thanks to the individual profit sharing\n• We will support you with a one-on-one coaching and trainings designed to help you develop your entrepreneurial skills\n• The competence cells structure, provides you with a strong meaningful and relevant network\n• The entrepreneurial lab: a playground for new ideas and a potential launching for start-ups",
